data.title: Sahasam Swasaga Sagipo’s latest collections
data.meta_description: Telugu cinema news, Movie reviews, OTT News, OTT Release dates, Latest Movie reviews in Telugu, telugu movie reviews, Box office collections
data.text:
Naga Chaitanya’s Sahasam Swasaga Sagipo released to some decent reviews all over. The Gautam Menon also had some decent openings in the metros and the latest news is that it has collected close to 2.2 crores on the first day of its release worldwide.

The film which turns into a suspense thriller has been well appreciated for Chay’s acting skills. A R Rahman’s music is yet another strong point of this film which has Manjima Mohan playing the female lead.

As the nation is struck with the currency ban, it would be interesting to see how the film fares from now on.
